        </td>
        <td width="60%" valign="middle">
          <h3 class="subsection-title">Historic Computers</h3>
          <p><b>Featured:</b> The <a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLnw98JPyObn3QSIwUz5Iv6NA1x-uGFqAa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Bendix G-15</a> - a programmable vacuum tube computer from 1956, possibly the oldest running computer in North America!</p>
